condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA | Description :All goods and works required for the project and to be financed out of the proceeds of theLoan shall be procured in accordance with the requirements in procurement guideline and legal document | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :LA | Description :Annual financial statements audited by independent auditors acceptable to the Bank. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA | Description :Before commencing works on any local road section:In case new roads are involved for thelocal road program, an EIA and EMP shall be prepared, in case of land acquisition, RAP is required. | Due Date :30-Jun-2015

Finance Agreement :LA | Description :Ningxia must maintain a financial management system and provide semiannual projectconsolidated financial statements in accordance with accounting standards acceptable to the Bank | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :LA | Description :The EMP, RAP, RFP, and ESF satisfactory to the Bank, will be applied to implement the project;| Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA | Description :The proceeds of the loan would be on-lent to Ningxia Autonomous Region on the same terms andconditions as the Bank loan, with Ningxia bearing the foreign exchange risk. | Due Date :30-Jun-2010
